\c 23
\s Jesu pamberi paPirato naHerodhe
\p
\v 1 Zvino chaunga chavo chose chikasimuka, vakamutungamirira kuna Pirato.
\p
\v 2 Zvino vakatanga kumupomera mhosva, vachiti: Takawana uyu achitsausa rudzi, achidzivisa kupa mutero kuna Kesari; achiti iye pachake ndiKristu Mambo.
\v 3 Ipapo Pirato akamubvunza achiti: Ko uri Mambo wavaJudha here? Akamupindura, akati: Unoreva iwe.
\v 4 Zvino Pirato akati kuvapristi vakuru nechaunga: Handiwani mhosva kumunhu uyu.
\v 5 Ivo vakanyanya kusimbisa, vachiti: Unomutsa vanhu, achidzidzisa muJudhiya rose, achitanga paGarirea kusvikira pano.
\p
\v 6 Pirato wakati anzwa zveGarirea, akabvunza kana munhu uyu ari muGarirea.
\v 7 Akangoti anzwa kuti ndoweushe hwaHerodhe, akamutumira kuna Herodhe, iye wakanga ari muJerusarema amene pamazuva iwayo.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Herodhe wakati achiona Jesu akafara kwazvo-kwazvo; nokuti waishuva kumuona kwe\add nguva\add* refu, nokuti wakanga anzwa zvinhu zvizhinji pamusoro pake; akatarisira kuti uchaona chimwe chiratidzo chingaitwa naye.
\v 9 Akamubvunza namashoko mazhinji; asi iye haana kumupindura chinhu.
\v 10 Zvino vapristi vakuru navanyori vakamira vakamupomera mhosva zvine simba.
\v 11 NaHerodhe namauto ake vakamuzvidza, nokusweveredza; vakazomupfekedza, nguvo dzinobwinya, vakamudzosera kuna Pirato.
\v 12 Nomusi iwoyo Pirato naHerodhe vakava shamwari; nokuti paimbova neruvengo pakati pavo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino Pirato wakati adanira pamwechete vapristi vakuru navatongi navanhu.
\v 14 akati kwavari: Mauya nomunhu uyu kwandiri sounotsausa vanhu; zvino tarirai ini ndabvunzisisa pamberi penyu, ndikasawana mumunhu uyu mhosva yezvinhu zvamunomupomera;
\v 15 kwete, kunyange naHerodhevo; nokuti ndinokutumaizve kwaari; zvino tarirai, hapana chakafanira rufu chakaitwa naye.
\v 16 Naizvozvo ndichamurova ndigo\add mu\add*sunungura.
\v 17 Nokuti waifanira kuvasunungurira umwe pamutambo.
\p
\v 18 Asi vose vakadanidzira pamwechete vachiti: Kure nouyu, mutisunungurire Bharabhasi!
\v 19 Iye wakanga akandirwa mutirongo nemhaka yerimwe bongozozo rakanga ramutswa muguta, nokuuraya.
\v 20 Zvino Pirato achida kusunungura Jesu, akataurazve kwavari.
\v 21 Asi ivo vakadanidzira, vachiti: Roverera pamuchinjikwa, muroverere pamuchinjikwa!
\v 22 Akati kwavari rwechitatu: Nemhaka yei, waita chakaipa chipi? Handina kuwana mhosva yorufu maari; naizvozvo ndichamurova ndigo\add mu\add*sunungura.
\v 23 Asi ivo vakasimbisa namanzwi makuru, vachikumbira kuti arovererwe pamuchinjikwa. Manzwi avo naavapristi vakuru akakunda.
\p
\v 24 Zvino Pirato akapa mutongo kuti zviitwe sezvavakakumbira;
\v 25 akavasunungurira uyo wavakakumbira, wakanga akandwa mutirongo nemhaka yebongozozo neyokuuraya; akakumikidza Jesu kuzvido zvavo.
\s Jesu unorovererwa pamuchinjikwa
\p
\v 26 Zvino vakati vachienda naye, vakabata mumwe, \add wainzi\add* Simoni muKurini, achibva kuruwa vakaisa muchinjikwa pamusoro pake, kuti atakure shure kwaJesu.
\p
\v 27 Akateverwa nechaunga chikuru, navakadzi vaimuririravo nokumuchema.
\v 28 Asi Jesu wakatendeukira kwavari, akati: Vakunda veJerusarema, musachema ini, asi muzvicheme imwi navana venyu;
\v 29 nokuti tarirai, mazuva anouya avachati nawo: Dzakaropafadzwa mhanje, nezvizvaro zvisina kutongobereka, namazamu asina kutongomwisa.
\v 30 Zvino vachatanga kuti kumakomo: Wirai pamusoro pedu; nokuzvikomo: Tifukidzei.
\v 31 Nokuti kana vachiita zvinhu izvi kumuti munyoro, zvinyi zvichaitwa kunowakawoma?
\p
\v 32 Zvino kwakanga kuna vamwe vaiti vezvakaipa vavirivo, kuti vaurawe pamwechete naye.
\p
\v 33 Zvino vakati vasvika panzvimbo inonzi Dehenya, ipapo vakamuroverera pamuchinjikwa navaiti vezvakaipa umwe kuruoko rworudyi nomumwe kuruboshwe.
\v 34 Ipapo Jesu akati: Baba, vakangamwirei, nokuti havazivi chavanoita. Vakagovana nguvo dzake, vachikanda mijenya.
\v 35 Vanhu vakamira, vakatarira. Navatongivo pamwechete navo vaka\add mu\add*sweveredza, vachiti: Wakaponesa vamwe; ngaazviponese; kana ari Kristu, musanangurwa waMwari.
\p
\v 36 Namautovo akamusweveredza, akauya \add kwaari\add* akamupa vhiniga,
\v 37 vachiti: Kana uri Mambo wavaJudha, zviponese.
\v 38 Zvino; kwakanga kuno rugwarovo rwakanyorwa pamusoro pake namavara echiGiriki nechiRoma nechiHebheru, \add rwaiti\add*: UYU NDIMAMBO WAVAJUDHA.
\p
\v 39 Zvino umwe wavaiti vezvakaipa vakanga vakaremberedzwa wakamutuka achiti: Kana uri Kristu, zviponese iwe nesu.
\v 40 Umwe akapindura, akamutsiura, achiti: Iwe hautyi kunyange naMwari kanhi, zvauri pakutongwa kumwe?
\v 41 Isu zvirokwazvo zvakatiruramira, nokuti isu tinogamuchira mubairo wemabasa edu; asi uyu haana kuita chinhu chisakafanira.
\v 42 Zvino akati kuna Jesu: Ishe mundirangarire kana masvika muushe hwenyu.
\v 43 Jesu akati kwaari: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwauri: Nhasi uchava neni muParadhiso.
\p
\v 44 Zvino yakanga yava nguva inenge yechitanhatu; kukavapo rima panyika yose, kusvikira paawa yepfumbamwe.
\v 45 Zuva rikasvibiswa, vheiri retembere rikabvaruka napakati.
\v 46 Zvino Jesu wakati adanidzira nenzwi guru, akati: Baba, mumaoko enyu ndinokumikidza mweya wangu; akati areva izvozvo, akapa mweya.
\p
\v 47 Ipapo mukuru wezana wakati aona zvakaitika, akarumbidza Mwari, achiti: Zvirokwazvo uyu wakanga ari munhu wakarurama.
\v 48 Vazhinji vose vakanga vakaungana kuzoona izvozvo, vakati vachiona zvakaitika, vakadzoka vachirova zvifuva zvavo.
\v 49 Navazikanwi vake vose, navakadzi vaimutevera vachibva Garirea, vakamira kure, vachiona zvinhu izvozvi.
\s Kuvigwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 50 Zvino tarira, murume wainzi Josefa, gurukota, murume wakanaka wakarurama;
\v 51 iye wakanga asina kutenderana navo pakurangana nokuita kwavo; \add waiva\add* weArimatia, guta ravaJudha, iyevo wakanga achimirira ushe hwaMwari;
\v 52 iye wakaenda kuna Pirato akandokumbira mutumbi waJesu,
\v 53 akauburusa, akauputira nemicheka yakapfava, akauradzika mubwiro bwakanga bwakacherwa pabwe, makanga musina kumbovigwa munhu.
\v 54 Zvino waiva musi wokugadzirira, sabata roswedera.
\v 55 Navakadzivo, vakanga vauya naye vachibva Garirea, vakatevera mumashure, vakaona bwiro, nomuisirwe womutumbi wake.
\v 56 Vakadzoka, vakagadzira zvinonhuhwira nezvizoro vakazorora nesabata sezvinoreva murairo.
